section.t:
The example below provide an overview of PCEP peer session informations and LSP-DB in the Yang Module. 




       +-------+                  +-------+ 
       |       |                  |       |  
       | PCC1  |<---------------->|       |
       |       |                  |       |
       +-------+                  |       |  
      IP:192.0.2.1                |       |  
                                  |  PCE  |  
                                  |       |  
       +-------+                  |       |  
       |       |                  |       |  
       | PCC2  |<---------------->|       |
       |       |                  |       |       
       +-------+                  |       |
      IP:192.0.2.2                |       |
                                  |       |  
                                  |       |  
       +-------+                  |       |  
       |       |                  |       |  
       | PCC4  |<---------------->|       |
       |       |                  |       |       
       +-------+                  |       |
      IP:2001:DB8::4              |       |                                                      
                                  +-------+
                                IP:192.0.2.3
                                   2001:DB8::3   

